rt content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1\"><link rel=icon href=/assets/favicon/favicon.ico sizes=any><link rel=icon type=image/svg+xml href=/assets/favicon/favicon.svg><link rel=apple-touch-icon href=/assets/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png><link rel=manifest href=/assets/favicon/manifest.json><link rel=stylesheet type=text/css href=/assets/css/style.b90fbce7a8ead63d7fa86b6f69db799e89a9ec2560747ae1f1fc443307d39f40.css></head><body class=fullscreen><section id=playground class=playground><div class=\"editor-lines hidden-mobile\"></div><pre class=editor></pre><codapi-snippet editor=external actions=Share:@share autosave></codapi-snippet></section><script src=https://codapi.org/modules/lz-string/lz-string.min.js></script><script type=module src=https://codapi.org/assets/playground.js></script><script defer src=https://codapi.org/modules/codapi/snippet.js></script></body></html>","expanded":true},{"id":"f89645477c99d931","topic":"https://txstc55.github.io/ugly-avatar/","expanded":true},{"id":"f896457956b49037","topic":"网站状态，异常即时邮件提醒","expanded":false,"children":[{"id":"f89da3a0e51fe489","topic":"<ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li>   <li></li> </ul> <pre   data-lang=\"bash\"   class=\"code-snippet__js\" ><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__meta\">#!/bin/bash  </span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">URL_LIST=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"www.baidu.com www.ctnrs.com www.der-matech.net.cn www.der-matech.com.cn www.der-matech.cn www.der-matech.top www.der-matech.org\"</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">for</span> URL <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL_LIST</span>; <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">do</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    FAIL_COUNT=0  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">for</span> ((i=1;i&lt;=3;i++)); <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">do</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        curl -s --head http://<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span> &gt; /dev/null  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        HTTP_CODE=$(curl -o /dev/null --connect-timeout 3 -s -w <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"%{http_code}\\n\"</span> http://<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span>)  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$HTTP_CODE</span> -eq 200 ]; <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">then</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">            <span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span> OK\"</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">            <span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">break</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">else</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">            <span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span> retry <span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$FAIL_COUNT</span>\"</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">            <span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">let</span> FAIL_COUNT++  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">fi</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">done</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$FAIL_COUNT</span> -eq 3 ]; <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">then</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        <span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Warning: <span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span> Access failure!\"</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">echo</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"网站<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span>坏掉，请及时处理\"</span>&nbsp;|&nbsp;mail&nbsp;-s&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$URL</span>网站高危\"</span>&nbsp;1242253055@qq.com&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">fi</span>  </span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">done</span></span></code></pre>","expanded":true}]},{"id":"f84f0cf3a6095583","topic":"https://github.com/seatrix/Keil-Array-Visualization/blob/master/Keil%20Array%20Visualization%20V1.pdf","expanded":false},{"id":"f89d242dcde74eaf","topic":"AlwaysMouseWheel ","expanded":true},{"id":"f89d24930c4f76ae","topic":"for (let i = 0; i <= 120; i++) {   setTimeout(() =>{save_file(),alert('savejsmind')}, 5*60*1000 * i) }","expanded":true},{"id":"f8af885285f7778a","topic":"ll /proc/进程ID/fd","expanded":true}]},{"id":"d974","topic":"Why jsMind?","expanded":false,"direction":"left","children":[{"id":"471a","topic":"Open Source","expanded":false},{"id":"693b","topic":"Fast and Faster","expanded":false},{"id":"1405","topic":"Simple and clear","expanded":false},{"id":"394a","topic":"Themes and custom style","expanded":false},{"id":"2a63","topic":"Free w/o Ads","expanded":false},{"id":"5e48","topic":"Only a browser is required","expanded":false},{"id":"b587","topic":"<ul dir=\"auto\"> <li>Resources: <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/docs\" rel=\"nofollow\">文档 - Documents</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/jsmind\" rel=\"nofollow\">NPM - jsmind</a></li> <li>CDN - <a href=\"/hizzgdev/jsmind/blob/master/docs/zh/1.usage.md\">用法</a> <a href=\"/hizzgdev/jsmind/blob/master/docs/en/1.usage.md\">Usage</a> <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/jsmind/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UNPKG</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/jsmind/\" rel=\"nofollow\">jsDelivr</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://jsd.onmicrosoft.cn/npm/jsmind/\" rel=\"nofollow\">jsDelivr 国内镜像</a></li> </ul> </li> </ul> </li> <li>Apps : <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://jsmind.online\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://jsmind.online</a></li> </ul> </li> <li>Demo : <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/1_basic.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">显示一个脑图 Render a mindmap</a> [<a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/1_basic_cn.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内版</a>]</li> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/2_features.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">试用所有功能 Try all features</a> [<a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/2_features_cn.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内版</a>]</li> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/3_requirejs.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">requirejs + jsMind</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/hizzgdev/jsmind-samples\">更多示例 - More samples</a> [<a href=\"https://gitee.com/hizzgdev/jsmind-samples\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内版</a>]</li> </ul> </li> </ul>","expanded":false,"background-color":"#f39c12","leading-line-color":"#e67e22"}]},{"id":"5b35","topic":"Use mouse","expanded":false,"direction":"left","children":[{"id":"d27d","topic":"Click node: select it","expanded":false},{"id":"4c7d","topic":"Double click node: edit mode, [Enter] to save","expanded":false},{"id":"9bc0","topic":"Drag node: place it","expanded":false},{"id":"5ad8","topic":"Click the little circle: expand/collapse children","expanded":false}]},{"id":"0b5c","topic":"Use keyboard","expanded":true,"direction":"left","children":[{"id":"1007","topic":"Enter: new brother node","expanded":false},{"id":"f389","topic":"Ctrl+Enter: new child node","expanded":false},{"id":"9b69","topic":"F2: edit mode","expanded":false},{"id":"15e3","topic":"Delete: delete node","expanded":false},{"id":"1565","topic":"Space: expand/collapse children","expanded":false},{"id":"27ca","topic":"You can customize the shortcuts","expanded":false}]},{"id":"f84a6c75aea1032b","topic":"20240517","expanded":false,"direction":"right","children":[{"id":"f84b9c8d2f7d8ffa","topic":"https://web.gistoapp.com/#/snippet/50bc04dcdbf0d794721f1b0754d0f740 ","expanded":false},{"id":"f84a77f264888092","topic":"Documents","expanded":false,"children":[{"id":"f84a879c45602a1e","topic":"<ul dir=\"auto\"> <li>Resources: <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/docs\" rel=\"nofollow\">文档 - Documents</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/jsmind\" rel=\"nofollow\">NPM - jsmind</a></li> <li>CDN - <a href=\"/hizzgdev/jsmind/blob/master/docs/zh/1.usage.md\">用法</a> <a href=\"/hizzgdev/jsmind/blob/master/docs/en/1.usage.md\">Usage</a> <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/jsmind/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UNPKG</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/jsmind/\" rel=\"nofollow\">jsDelivr</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://jsd.onmicrosoft.cn/npm/jsmind/\" rel=\"nofollow\">jsDelivr 国内镜像</a></li> </ul> </li> </ul> </li> <li>Apps : <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://jsmind.online\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://jsmind.online</a></li> </ul> </li> <li>Demo : <ul dir=\"auto\"> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/1_basic.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">显示一个脑图 Render a mindmap</a> [<a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/1_basic_cn.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内版</a>]</li> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/2_features.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">试用所有功能 Try all features</a> [<a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/2_features_cn.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内版</a>]</li> <li><a href=\"https://hizzgdev.github.io/jsmind/example/3_requirejs.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">requirejs + jsMind</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/hizzgdev/jsmind-samples\">更多示例 - More samples</a> [<a href=\"https://gitee.com/hizzgdev/jsmind-samples\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内版</a>]</li> </ul> </li> </ul>","expanded":false}]},{"id":"f84b9dd31c6fd574","topic":"三十年，解决人生三大问题","expanded":true,"children":[{"id":"f85d12c9dba95ba0","topic":"三十年，解决人生三大问题 我最近看到一篇文章，很有意思，分享给大家。 文章大意是，人的一生就是解决三个基本问题：事业、家庭和财务。 一份有成就的事业，一个幸福的家庭，一个健康的财务状况，人生就没有遗憾了。 我们的人生规划，就是朝着解决这三个问题努力。哪怕其中只有一个没有解决，你的人生就过不好。  原文作者提出了他的规划。他说，这三个问题要分阶段解决，每个阶段重点解决一个问题。而且他估计，每个阶段要花费十年，总共需要三十年。  （1）第一个十年。你搞清楚自己想干什么，找到方向，为事业打下基础，从此全力投入。  （2）第二个十年。你结婚、买房、养育后代。  （3）第三个十年。你努力赚钱，积蓄退休金。  如果将18岁成年作为起点，过完这三个十年，你就已经48岁了。  也就是说，你的目标是，到了48岁，基本解决人生三大问题。48岁以后的时间，就是自己的选择，追求梦想，照顾家人，或者继续推进事业，积累更多财富。","expanded":false}]},{"id":"f84b9d4a0c5c8e02","topic":"http://localhost:3044/#/","expanded":false},{"id":"f84b9d0eb2393014","topic":"https://gojs.net/latest/samples/         ","expanded":true},{"id":"f84b9d70bdc6ebe7","topic":"blob:https://hizzgdev.github.io/39c96e12-37c6-4035-83ef-45dec1233fec","expanded":false},{"id":"f84f0d541810a5fb","topic":"New Node","expanded":false},{"id":"f84f0d27c3837093","topic":"New Node","expanded":false}]}]}}